<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>태범프레시 × 카페24 | 플랫폼 전환 제안서</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+KR:wght@300;400;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700;900&family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --fresh-green: #1a7a4a;
    --fresh-green-light: #2aaa68;
    --fresh-green-pale: #e8f7ef;
    --fresh-orange: #f07d2a;
    --cafe24-blue: #0064ff;
    --dark: #0d1a0f;
    --mid: #2d4a35;
    --text: #1c2e20;
    --text-light: #5a7a62;
    --white: #ffffff;
    --cream: #f8faf8;
    --border: #d4e8da;
    --shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(26,122,74,0.10);
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--text);
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ─── NAV ─── */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    height: 60px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 0 32px;
  }
  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--fresh-green);
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
  }
  .nav-logo span { color: var(--dark); }
  .nav-links {
    display: flex; gap: 4px;
    list-style: none;
  }
  .nav-links a {
    font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-light);
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { background: var(--fresh-green-pale); color: var(--fresh-green); }
  .nav-cta {
    background: var(--fresh-green);
    color: white !important;
    padding: 8px 20px !important;
    border-radius: 24px !important;
    font-weight: 700 !important;
    font-size: 0.78rem !important;
    transition: all 0.2s !important;
  }
  .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--fresh-green-light) !important; transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(26,122,74,0.3) !important; }

  /* ─── PROGRESS BAR ─── */
  #progress-bar {
    position: fixed; top: 60px; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 99;
    height: 3px; background: rgba(26,122,74,0.1);
  }
  #progress-fill {
    height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--fresh-green), var(--fresh-green-light));
    width: 0%; transition: width 0.1s;
  }

  /* ─── HERO ─── */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: var(--dark);
    position: relative;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;
    padding: 120px 64px 80px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 70% at 80% 50%, rgba(26,122,74,0.25) 0%, transparent 70%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 50% at 10% 80%, rgba(42,170,104,0.12) 0%, transparent 60%);
  }
  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    background: rgba(26,122,74,0.3);
    border: 1px solid rgba(42,170,104,0.4);
    color: #6be6a8;
    font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    width: fit-content;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease both;
  }
  .hero-badge::before { content: '●'; font-size: 0.5rem; animation: pulse 2s infinite; }
  @keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1} 50%{opacity:0.3} }
  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.1s ease both;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.2s ease both;
  }
  .hero h1 em {
    font-style: normal;
    color: #6be6a8;
  }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 540px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.3s ease both;
  }
  .hero-stats {
    display: flex; gap: 40px;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.4s ease both;
  }
  .hero-stat-item { }
  .hero-stat-num {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    color: #6be6a8;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .hero-stat-label {
    font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
    margin-top: 4px;
  }
  .hero-scroll {
    position: absolute; bottom: 40px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.8s ease both;
  }
  .hero-scroll span { animation: scrollDown 2s infinite; }
  @keyframes scrollDown { 0%,100%{transform:translateY(0);opacity:1} 50%{transform:translateY(6px);opacity:0.5} }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  /* ─── SECTIONS ─── */
  section { padding: 96px 64px; }

  .section-tag {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--fresh-green); text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .section-tag::before { content: ''; width: 20px; height: 2px; background: var(--fresh-green); }

  h2.section-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.6rem);
    font-weight: 600; color: var(--dark);
    line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .section-desc {
    font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.8; max-width: 560px;
    margin-bottom: 56px;
  }

  /* ─── PAIN SECTION ─── */
  .pain-section { background: white; }
  .pain-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 48px;
  }
  .pain-card {
    background: var(--cream);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 28px;
    position: relative;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  .pain-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: var(--shadow); }
  .pain-icon {
    width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 12px;
    background: #fff3e8;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .pain-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--dark); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .pain-card p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-light); line-height: 1.7; }
  .pain-card .pain-tag {
    position: absolute; top: 20px; right: 20px;
    background: #fef3e7; color: #c8601a;
    font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 700;
    padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 12px;
  }

  /* ─── DIAGNOSIS ─── */
  .diagnosis-section { background: var(--dark); color: white; }
  .diagnosis-section .section-title { color: white; }
  .diagnosis-section .section-tag { color: #6be6a8; }
  .diagnosis-section .section-tag::before { background: #6be6a8; }
  .diag-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 32px;
  }
  .diag-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 20px; padding: 32px;
  }
  .diag-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: white; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .score-row {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .score-label { font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); width: 110px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .score-bar-bg { flex: 1; height: 8px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; }
  .score-bar { height: 100%; border-radius: 4px; transition: width 1s ease; }
  .score-bar.green { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1a7a4a, #2aaa68); }
  .score-bar.orange { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #c8601a, #f07d2a); }
  .score-bar.blue { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #0040aa, #0064ff); }
  .score-val { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; color: white; width: 36px; text-align: right; }

  .insight-box {
    background: rgba(107,230,168,0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(107,230,168,0.2);
    border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; margin-top: 20px;
  }
  .insight-box p { font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); line-height: 1.7; }

  /* ─── SOLUTION ─── */
  .solution-section { background: var(--fresh-green-pale); }
  .solution-header {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 64px; align-items: start; margin-bottom: 64px;
  }
  .solution-cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 20px; }
  .sol-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 28px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: all 0.3s;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .sol-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--fresh-green), var(--fresh-green-light));
  }
  .sol-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: var(--shadow); }
  .sol-num {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 3rem; color: var(--fresh-green-pale);
    position: absolute; top: 16px; right: 20px;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .sol-card-icon { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .sol-card h3 { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--dark); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .sol-card p { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--text-light); line-height: 1.7; }
  .sol-card .benefit {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px;
    margin-top: 12px;
    font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--fresh-green);
    background: var(--fresh-green-pale); padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 12px;
  }
  .benefit::before { content: '↑'; }

  /* ─── COMPARE ─── */
  .compare-section { background: white; }
  .compare-table {
    width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;
    border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    margin-top: 48px;
  }
  .compare-table thead tr {
    background: var(--dark); color: white;
  }
  .compare-table th {
    padding: 20px 24px; text-align: left;
    font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }
  .compare-table th:first-child { width: 30%; }
  .compare-table th.highlight { background: var(--fresh-green); }
  .compare-table tbody tr:nth-child(even) { background: var(--cream); }
  .compare-table tbody tr:nth-child(odd) { background: white; }
  .compare-table tbody tr:hover { background: var(--fresh-green-pale); }
  .compare-table td {
    padding: 16px 24px; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .compare-table td:first-child { font-weight: 600; color: var(--dark); }
  .check { color: var(--fresh-green); font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; }
  .cross { color: #d44; font-size: 1rem; }
  .highlight-cell { background: rgba(26,122,74,0.06) !important; font-weight: 600; color: var(--fresh-green) !important; }

  /* ─── ROADMAP ─── */
  .roadmap-section { background: var(--cream); }
  .roadmap-timeline {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 48px;
    margin-top: 48px;
  }
  .roadmap-timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; left: 16px; top: 0; bottom: 0;
    width: 2px; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--fresh-green), transparent);
  }
  .roadmap-item {
    position: relative; margin-bottom: 40px;
    opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease both;
  }
  .roadmap-item:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
  .roadmap-item:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .roadmap-item:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
  .roadmap-dot {
    position: absolute; left: -40px; top: 6px;
    width: 16px; height: 16px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--fresh-green);
    border: 3px solid white;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--fresh-green);
  }
  .roadmap-period {
    font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--fresh-green); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .roadmap-item h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--dark); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .roadmap-item p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-light); line-height: 1.7; }
  .roadmap-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-top: 12px; }
  .rtag {
    font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 500;
    padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 12px;
    background: white; border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text-light);
  }

  /* ─── CTA FINAL ─── */
  .cta-section {
    background: var(--dark);
    text-align: center; padding: 120px 64px;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .cta-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 60% at 50% 50%, rgba(26,122,74,0.3) 0%, transparent 70%);
  }
  .cta-section * { position: relative; }
  .cta-pretitle {
    font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: #6be6a8; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .cta-section h2 {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    color: white; line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .cta-section p {
    font-size: 1rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    line-height: 1.8; max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto 48px;
  }
  .cta-btns { display: flex; gap: 16px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    background: var(--fresh-green);
    color: white;
    padding: 16px 36px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--fresh-green-light); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(26,122,74,0.4); }
  .btn-secondary {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    color: white;
    padding: 16px 36px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); transform: translateY(-2px); }

  /* ─── FOOTER ─── */
  footer {
    background: #060e08;
    padding: 48px 64px;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 24px;
  }
  .footer-brand {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
  }
  .footer-info { font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); line-height: 1.8; }
  .footer-contact { font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45); text-align: right; line-height: 1.8; }

  /* ─── UTILS ─── */
  .container { max-width: 1120px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .two-col { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 64px; align-items: start; }

  /* ─── HIGHLIGHT BOX ─── */
  .key-number-box {
    background: var(--fresh-green);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 40px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .key-number-box .big-num {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 4rem; line-height: 1;
    color: #6be6a8;
  }
  .key-number-box p { font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.8; margin-top: 8px; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    section { padding: 64px 24px; }
    .hero { padding: 100px 24px 64px; }
    .pain-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .diag-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .solution-header { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 32px; }
    .solution-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    nav { padding: 0 16px; }
    .nav-links { display: none; }
    footer { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
    .footer-contact { text-align: center; }
    .hero-stats { gap: 24px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">태범프레시 <span>× 카페24</span></div>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#pain">현황 진단</a></li>
    <li><a href="#diagnosis">성장 분석</a></li>
    <li><a href="#solution">카페24 솔루션</a></li>
    <li><a href="#compare">비교</a></li>
    <li><a href="#roadmap">전환 로드맵</a></li>
    <li><a href="#cta" class="nav-cta">미팅 신청</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<div id="progress-bar"><div id="progress-fill"></div></div>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div style="max-width:900px;">
    <div class="hero-badge">맞춤 플랫폼 전환 제안서</div>
    <p class="hero-eyebrow">태범프레시 hongikmarket.co.kr</p>
    <h1>
      검증된 맛, 이제<br>
      <em>성장을 위한 인프라</em>를<br>
      갖출 때입니다
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      신선 간편식·밀키트 시장에서 입지를 굳힌 태범프레시.
      브랜드 자산은 충분합니다. 지금 필요한 건
      이 성장을 뒷받침할 확장 가능한 쇼핑몰 인프라입니다.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="hero-stat-item">
        <div class="hero-stat-num">200만+</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-label">카페24 입점 브랜드</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stat-item">
        <div class="hero-stat-num">0원</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-label">기본 솔루션 월 이용료</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stat-item">
        <div class="hero-stat-num">#1</div>
        <div class="hero-stat-label">국내 자사몰 플랫폼</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-scroll">
    SCROLL <span>↓</span>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PAIN -->
<section class="pain-section" id="pain">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-tag">현황 진단</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">지금 쇼핑몰이<br>성장의 발목을 잡고 있습니다</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">
      홍익마켓(hongikmarket.co.kr)을 분석한 결과, 위드소프트 기반의 현재 플랫폼은
      브랜드 성장에 따른 기능 확장과 마케팅 자동화에 구조적 한계를 보이고 있습니다.
    </p>
    <div class="pain-grid">
      <div class="pain-card">
        <div class="pain-tag">확장성 이슈</div>
        <div class="pain-icon">📦</div>
        <h3>멀티채널 연동의 한계</h3>
        <p>네이버 스마트스토어, 쿠팡, 오픈마켓 등 멀티채널 통합 관리가 어려워 재고와 주문이 분산됩니다. 운영 효율이 떨어지고 실수 리스크가 높아집니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pain-card">
        <div class="pain-tag">마케팅 제약</div>
